{"id":1200,"date":"2024-08-03T18:57:42","date_gmt":"2024-08-03T18:57:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1200"},"modified":"2024-09-24T21:30:00","modified_gmt":"2024-09-24T21:30:00","slug":"mission-013","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-013\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #013: Basic Literacy"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #013: Basic Literacy<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Dresco Town &#8211; man in beanie on southern tip<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Dresco Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Read all 45 Trainer Tips signs in the game <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Notebook<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A young aspiring punk rocker who can\u2019t read wants you to demonstrate your reading skills by finding and reading all 45 Trainer Tips signs across Borrius. Doing so will get you the Notebook, an item required to upgrade the Stat Scanner into a mobile Move Tutor.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/013\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-illiterate-man.jpg\" alt=\"The illiterate man \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The illiterate man<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>South of Jax and Arthur\u2019s house in Dresco Town, on the southern tip, is a man who has a reading problem.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/013\/02-pokemon-unbound-all-45-signs-must-be-read.jpg\" alt=\"All 45 signs must be read \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>All 45 signs must be read<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>He wants you to read all the Trainer Tips signs in Borrius &#8211; there are 45 of them, and they are spread all over Borrius.<\/p>\n<p>You can accept this mission at any time, but you will not be able to complete this mission until after beating the Pok\u00e9mon League, because only then will Redwood Forest and Cube Corp. be available.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>As you read Trainer Tip signs, their number and location will be recorded in the Mission Log so you can remember which ones you\u2019ve read before and how many you are yet to find.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/013\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-mission-log-will-keep-track-of-the-ones-you-have-found.jpg\" alt=\"The Mission Log will keep track of the ones you have found \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Mission Log will keep track of the ones you have found<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>A full list of signs and their locations are below:<\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table left grey\" style=\"min-width:760px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" class=\"text-large center\">Trainer Tips Sign Locations<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Sign #<\/th>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<th>Screenshot<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"min-width:120px;\">\n        <strong>Trainer Tips<br \/>\n        Sign #01<\/strong>\n      <\/td>\n<td>\n        <strong>Frozen Heights<\/strong><br \/>\n        West of Player\u2019s House\n      <\/td>\n<td>\n<figure class=\"img-modal\"><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/013\/04-pokemon-unbound-trainer-tips-sign-location-01.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/013\/04-pokemon-unbound-trainer-tips-sign-location-01.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Trainer Tips<br \/>\n        Sign #02<\/strong>\n      <\/td>\n<td>\n        <strong>Route 1<\/strong><br \/>\